{"tid":1459972,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"昨日機場一役 Lesson learnt","createTime":"2019-08-13T00:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T07:35:25.000Z","uid":126436,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"feb96f257a0edd8bbabbf1d01ab2f9b4cc164f41","tid":1459972,"uid":126436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:17:20.000Z","msg":"1. 以尋日計 狗同政府的確無我地乎<br />\n-&gt; 機場接機送機 係有戰術影響力 而又相對安全<br />\n2. 謠言及恐慌 威力其實都好大<br />\n-&gt; 事實上 1800機場真係closing 機組人員 地勤都嗌人走<br />\n* 反而尋日係吹起唔同既風向 嚇到d人走哂 <br />\nE.g. 熄燈 停機場快綫 幾點幾點清場<br />\n<br />\n（及後 如果有咁既情況發生 我地要有個一致 明確方向 同做法，而唔係受唔同資訊影響。資訊流通只可作參考，一定要參考後評估到做決策)<br />\n<br />\n3. 政府同狗 唔係冇做野<br />\n-&gt; 製造輿論 帶風向 話機場係非法集結<br />\n-&gt; 而狗真係有出動入左機場內部 甚至放undercover<br />\n* 只係差在佢未郁手先 <br />\n<br />\n(大家都一定要考慮到 政府唔會罷手 由你自由出入機場，我地都要有預防措施同即時對策兩部份）<br />\n<br />\n4. 最後一點 昨日事件再次證明「冇狗 冇暴力」<br />\n-&gt;政府識有意識地 同潛意識地 洗人地腦我地都要識<br />\n(文宣 記者會 一定要以最簡單既文字表達到成個logic)<br />\n<br />\n理想主義d，以尋日個方向發展<br />\n- 對友方無損傷<br />\n- 做到影響 渣政府春袋<br />\n- Be Water 適時要走要留 （參考立法會一役）<br />\n- Be Humble 全民有禮 （立場唔同，先尊重，後各有各做）<br />\n<br />\n手機打唔到幾多，靠各位巴絲繼續比意見。<br />\n有錯請指出，大家一齊求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49fd5aff2e523803fd00aa887359930d6fd88686","tid":1459972,"uid":126436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:18:50.000Z","msg":"喂 幫手推推呀"},{"pid":"c1e279689f7150cab93d898988abc9463399e993","tid":1459972,"uid":126436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:19:33.000Z","msg":"推yo"},{"pid":"eba82934109b1b7e61ee5abc38f49d82b14f259f","tid":1459972,"uid":126436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:19:43.000Z","msg":"Hey"},{"pid":"9706f8fa6e4ca7c594f110934af1ca38c4566212","tid":1459972,"uid":126436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:20:31.000Z","msg":"What&rsquo;s up"},{"pid":"dd7593109c670e24d32feb27a80211421b79d6ac","tid":1459972,"uid":126436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:23:43.000Z","msg":"剩係評分 講下野丫-.-"},{"pid":"3d7dfa64b458565f243f78d532e196696b340fdc","tid":1459972,"uid":126436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:25:10.000Z","msg":"Flexibility and mobility is key to lift heavier weights."},{"pid":"6fc8d2e0ea418fee134f67e793b352eb74e840f3","tid":1459972,"uid":126436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:27:52.000Z","msg":"Be humble means no hostility and remaining a calm and serious mindset."},{"pid":"6a09512edcd73969c09c31df7c70c78d7e33a4a7","tid":1459972,"uid":126436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:30:16.000Z","msg":"團結呀 尊重呀"},{"pid":"30a7b854269f70a872a04d458e6e1b303ef801b7","tid":1459972,"uid":126436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:32:25.000Z","msg":"自推一二三"},{"pid":"6950f0e6fa8b4cb99ead63d08a293a0e73760a6f","tid":1459972,"uid":126436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:15:39.000Z","msg":"單機緊 anyway, 逼到林鄭講返人話"},{"pid":"de5cd72490831588849b1330c5fd3ec9338ed83a","tid":1459972,"uid":270196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}